## Naming
- Variables and functions: camelCase
- Components: PascalCase
- Files: kebab-case
- Constants: SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE
- Types: PascalCase, no I prefix
- Booleans: prefix is, has, can
- Event handlers: prefix handle
- Async functions: name what they return, not that it fetches

## Rules
- No hardcoded values anywhere — all magic values go in /constants/index.ts
- No any in TypeScript. No @ts-ignore. No as SomeType unless unavoidable.
- All shared types in /lib/types.ts only.
- Tailwind only — no custom CSS, no inline style={{}}. Semantic color tokens only, no hex.
- No console.log — console.error inside catch blocks only.
- No API keys in code — process.env only.
- No function longer than ~40 lines — split it.
- No logic duplication — extract to /lib.
